      "title": "WAVE03: Decouple markets, bets, and math from the legacy models package",
      "status": "pending",
      "prompt": "Using the WAVE03 boundary seams, remove direct `socialpredict/models` dependencies from the internal markets, bets, and math packages as far as practical. Push translation toward repositories or narrow boundary helpers, preserve existing behavior, and update tests. This wave should make the core business/domain layer less persistence-shaped before the API contract work lands.",
      "working_dir": "../socialpredict/backend",
      "depends_on": [
